title: Vaccine Distribution and Potential Holiday Spikes
itunes:title: Vaccine Distribution and Potential Holiday Spikes
description:
Dr. Bruce Farber, Chief of Infectious Diseases at Northwell Health, discusses COVID-19 vaccine distribution and potential coronavirus spikes over the holidays.

Host: Carol Massar. Producer: Doni Holloway.
